name: LargeApp
desc: A large application that requires extra pages

approval.teal:
#pragma version 10
txn ApplicationID
int 0
==
bnz create
int 1
return
create:
// Add enough bytecode to require extra pages
byte "This is a large application that requires extra program pages to demonstrate schema breaking changes."
pop
byte "More padding to increase the program size beyond a single page."
pop
byte "Extra pages are considered a breaking change because they affect the minimum balance requirement."
pop
byte "When an app requires more pages, it needs more Algos to maintain minimum balance."
pop
byte "This makes it incompatible with the previous version."
pop
byte "Padding line 1: Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit."
pop
byte "Padding line 2: Sed do eiusmod tempor incididunt ut labore et dolore magna aliqua."
pop
byte "Padding line 3: Ut enim ad minim veniam, quis nostrud exercitation ullamco laboris."
pop
byte "Padding line 4: Duis aute irure dolor in reprehenderit in voluptate velit esse."
pop
byte "Padding line 5: Excepteur sint occaecat cupidatat non proident, sunt in culpa."
pop
byte "Padding line 6: Nemo enim ipsam voluptatem quia voluptas sit aspernatur aut odit."
pop
byte "Padding line 7: Neque porro quisquam est, qui dolorem ipsum quia dolor sit amet."
pop
byte "Padding line 8: At vero eos et accusamus et iusto odio dignissimos ducimus."
pop
byte "Padding line 9: Et harum quidem rerum facilis est et expedita distinctio."
pop
byte "Padding line 10: Temporibus autem quibusdam et aut officiis debitis aut rerum."
pop
int 1
return
